            sourceSnippet2: 'Summer Davos Forum opens in China as Premier Li Qiang highlights innovation, international cooperation — Anadolu Agency',
            source3: 'Modern Diplomacy',
            sourceUrl3: 'https://moderndiplomacy.eu/2026/06/24/china-defends-huawei-and-tech-growth-as-premier-rejects-subsidy-claims/',
            sourceSnippet3: 'China Defends Huawei and Tech Growth as Premier Rejects Subsidy Claims — Modern Diplomacy, 24 Juni 2026',
            source4: 'China Consulate Cape Town',
            sourceUrl4: 'https://capetown.china-consulate.gov.cn/eng/zgyw/202606/t20260624_11951579.htm',
            sourceSnippet4: 'Li Qiang Meets with ROK Prime Minister Kim Minseok — China Consulate, 23 Juni 2026'
